WINGS OF FLURRY
	SCHOOL:Evocation	DESCRIPTOR:Force
	CLASSES:Sorcerer=4
Components: V, S
Casting Time: 1 standard action
Range: 30 ft.
Area: 30-ft.-radius burst
Duration: Instantaneous
Saving Throw: Refl ex half
Spell Resistance: Yes
Immense, scaled wings unfurl from
behind you and beat at nearby foes in a
savage fl urry before vanishing as quickly
as they appeared.
You evoke fl ickering dragon’s wings
that strike at every target in range,
dealing 1d6 points of damage per
caster level to all designated targets
within 30 feet that fail a Refl ex saving
throw and half that damage to creatures
that succeed on the save.
Creatures that fail the Refl ex save
are also dazed for 1 round.
Special: A dragonblooded character,
or a character with the dragon type,
casts this spell at +1 caster level.




